Rating: 4
This recipe will accompany any meet, from fish to sausages (even lamb). It is a good departure from the traditional potatoes, rice or regular pasta. My friends were quite delighted when they tried it for the first time in their lives. I really recommend it. What I love the most is the twist over the regular spaetzle... this one adds color and flavor!!